text: Manak is a town in the Punjab province of Pakistan. It is in Lahore District at 31°13'0N 73°12'30E with an altitude of 173 metres (570 feet).Location of Manak - Falling Rain Genomics Neighbouring settlements include Phadiara, Singh Khalsa and Ghator. ==References== Category:Populated places in Lahore District
